<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 5: 240 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.1">苦成家父事厲公爲士,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.2">序行正迅強,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.3">以見惡於厲公.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.4">厲公亡道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.5">虐於百豫.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-1a.6">百豫反之.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.2 (STRIPS 1-6) MACHENGYUAN 5: 240, 245 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.1">苦成家父以其族三郤正百豫,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.2">不思使反.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.3">躬與舉士居官,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.4">旦夕治之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.5">使有君【1】臣之節.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.6">三郤中位,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.7">以正上下之過,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-2a.8">強於公家.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.3 (STRIPS 6-7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 245, 246 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.1">欒書欲作難,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.2">害三郤.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.3">謂苦成家父曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.4">“爲此世也從事,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.5">何以如是其疾與哉?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.6">於言有之:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.7">‘顑頷以至於今哉【6】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.8">亡道政也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.9">伐宅适.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-3a.10">吾子圖之.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.4 (STRIP 7) MACHENGYUAN 5: 246 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.1">苦成家父曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.2">“吾敢欲顑頷以事世哉?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.3">吾直立徑行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.4">遠慮圖後.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.5">雖不當世,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.6">苟義,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.7">毋久立死</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-4a.8">何傷哉!”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.5 (STRIPS 7-8) MACHENGYUAN 5: 246, 247 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.1">欒書【7】乃退,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.2">言於厲公曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.3">“三郤家厚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.4">取主君之衆</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.5">以不聽命,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.6">將大害.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.7">公懼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-5a.8">乃命長魚 矯【8】[...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.6 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 5: 241, 242 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.1">郤錡聞之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.2">告苦成家父曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.3">“以吾族三郤與【2】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.4">[...] 於君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.5">幸</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.6">則晉邦之社稷可得而事也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.7">不幸</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.8">則取免而出.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-6a.9">諸侯畜我,</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.7 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 5: 242, 243 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.1">苦成家父曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.2">“不可.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.3">君貴我而授我衆,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.4">以我爲能治.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.5">今【3】吾亡能治也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.6">而因以害君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.7">不義,刑莫大焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.8">雖得免而出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.9">以不能事君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.10">天下爲君者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-7a.11">誰欲畜汝諸哉?</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.8 (STRIPS 4-5) MACHENGYUAN 5: 243, 244 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.1">初,吾強立治衆,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.2">欲以長建主君</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.3">而御【4】難.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.4">今主君不於吾,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.5">故而反惡之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.6">吾毋有施政公事,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.7">雖死,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.8">焉逃之?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.9">吾聞爲臣者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.10">必使君得志於己</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-8a.11">而有後生.”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.KUCHENGJIAFU 5.24.9 (STRIPS 5, 9) MACHENGYUAN 5: 244, 248 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.1">苦成家父乃寧百豫.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.2">不使從【5】己蒞於廷.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.3">長魚矯策;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.4">自公所,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.5">拘人於百豫以入,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.6">囚之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.7">苦成家父捕長魚矯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.8">梏者諸廷,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0053_tls_001-9a.9">與其妻,與其母.</seg>
                </p>

